Very good price on wonderful wallpapers.  One thing that I've wanted for a while was a way to have my phone switch wallpapers automatically. I've finally found a way to do this with the app Automagic. I have all 6 of my Maxelus wallpapers in a Flow for Automagic and have it set up to change to a random wallpaper every hour and a half. With the in-app random settings of all of Maxelus' live wallpapers set to change every half hour, I always have a fresh, random scene to greet me.   Keep making your live wallpapers like this and you'll have a customer for life right here. Awesome work.
